Amity University Noida has been recognised for its excellence in various fields by NIRF 2024, outperforming other institutes in parameters such as Teaching, Graduation Outcome, Inclusivity & Research, as well as fostering an exceptional learning environment. Amity University Noida's rankings in 'Overall' category have shown a fluctuating trend as per the rankings of the previous years. In 2024, Amity University Noida climbed 8 ranks to #49 rank in the 'Overall' category by the NIRF ranking.

It has been seen that within the category of 'Overall', the institute's ranking has fallen when compared with the previous year's ranking. In 2024, Amity University Noida fell 94 ranks to #151 rank in the 'Overall' category by the NIRF ranking. This is the second consecutive year that the institute has slipped in the rankings.

The institute has displayed a fluctuating trend in the 'University' category as compared to the ranking of preceding years. In 2024, Amity University Noida climbed 3 ranks to #32 rank in the 'University' category by the NIRF ranking.

In the 'University' category, the institute's ranks have descended when compared with the previous year's ranking. In 2024, Amity University Noida fell 116 ranks to #151 rank in the 'University' category by the NIRF ranking. This is the second consecutive year that the institute has slipped in the rankings.

Amity Noida Rankings FAQs

Below mentioned are Amity Noida Ranking FAQs:

Q: What is the ranking of Amity University, Noida in the world?

A: 

Amity University Noida World Ranking given by QS for 2024 is 1001-1200. Out of most of the international ranking bodies, only QS has released rankings for 2024. Some of the other ranking bodies that have ranked Amity University Noida are THE (Times Higher Education), US News Rank (Category), and others. 1001-1200 is fairly a good rank.

Upvote

Q: What is the rank of Amity University, Noida in NIRF 2023?

A: 

Amity University Noida ranking NIRF 2023 under the Pharmacy category is 21, under the Management category is 28, under the Engineering category is 31, under the University category is 35, under the Research category is 45, and under the Overall category is 57. Hence, Amity University Noida is not only one of the top-ranked universities but is also ranked in almost all the NIRF ranking categories.

Upvote

Q: Is Amity a Tier 3 college?

A: 

Amity University Noida is one of the top-ranked private universities in India. Amity University Noida is ranked by top-ranking bodies like NIRF (National Institutional Ranking Framework), IIRF (Indian Institutional Ranking Framework), India Today, and others. QS mentions this university as one of the top leading universities. For Tier 3 college and university details, please visit the official website of the university.

Q: What is the ranking of Amity University, Noida in India?

A: 

Famous ranking bodies such as India Today, NIRF, Times, Outlook, and others have featured Amity University Noida in their list of top 100 universities. The university is ranked #30 by NIRF in the Engineering category. NIRF has ranked Amity University 21 under the Pharmacy category. A: 

 Amity School of Engineering and Technology has received a 634.47 score in 2023 which is quite good.
